name: generalHeaderBlocks
description: Number of additional blocks in General Header

name: recordLength
description: Record length from time zero (in increments of 0.5 times 1.024 s).

name: channelSetsPerScanType
description: Number of channel sets per scan type (1-99)

description: Skew fields length (0-99). Number of 32 byte extensions to scan type header

description: Extended header length (0-99). Number of 32 byte extensions to general header

name: externalHeaderBlocks
description: External header length (0-99). Number of 32 byte extensions to general header
